# Node sidecar binaries for Tauri's externalBin, provisioned per target triple by
# scripts/provision-node.mjs (local: copy the running Node 24; CI: --fetch from
# nodejs.org). Real binaries are ~tens of MB and platform-specific — never
# committed. cargo check does not need them; `tauri build` does, so provision
# first. Only this .gitignore + README.md are tracked.
node-*
!.gitignore
!README.md
